Message.Body:
Dear User,
A blacklisted IP address has been identified in your network. Immediate action is required to prevent potential security breaches.
Details:
- IP: @{triggerBody()?['Entity']?['properties']?['Address']}
- Country Name: @{body('Query_IP')?['country']}
- Country Code: @{body('Query_IP')?['countryCode']}
- ISP: @{body('CHECK_Endpoint')?['data']?['isp']}
- Domain: @{body('CHECK_Endpoint')?['data']?['domain']}
- IP Confidence Score: @{body('CHECK_Endpoint')?['data']?['abuseConfidenceScore']}
SOC Recommendations:
Block the source IP if it does not fall under your business requirements.
Disclaimer:
Please validate the object before proceeding with approval to ensure it aligns with business needs.
